- **Question:** What profile slug for the SRS Story 1 canonical test fixture?
- **Choice:** `cedar-ridge-automotive` (existing on production volume from prior V0–V10 validation work) for the new consultative run; existing artifacts there will be archived under `archive/v0-v10-historical/` per AC.13.5.
