- **Choice:** Studio admin `duane` (operator's own credential) authorizes my PRs because operator is the GitHub repo owner of Huminic/Hermes-Studio and I have operator's explicit per-tranche merge approval per D-003.
- **Audit:** every merge logs into the engagement log with PR number, commit SHA, deploy outcome.

